# 詞: 睇怕

1. 睇怕聽日都會落雨，記得帶遮啦。(It looks like it's going to rain tomorrow, remember to bring an umbrella.)

2. 佢成日遲到，睇怕今次都唔會準時。(He's always late, I'm afraid he won't be on time this time either.)

3. 呢間餐廳咁多人排隊，睇怕要等成個鐘。(There's such a long queue at this restaurant, it looks like we'll have to wait for an hour.)

4. 阿明最近日日OT，睇怕佢好快就會病倒。(Ah Ming has been working overtime every day lately, I'm afraid he'll fall sick soon.)

5. 睇怕呢單生意都係做唔成，對方根本冇誠意。(It looks like this deal won't go through, the other party has no sincerity at all.)

6. 股市咁波動，睇怕好多人會輸錢。(The stock market is so volatile, I'm afraid many people will lose money.)

7. 佢哋兩個成日嗌交，睇怕呢段感情維持唔到幾耐。(They argue all the time, I'm afraid this relationship won't last long.)

8. 睇怕呢間公司都係捱唔到今年，已經裁咗咁多人。(It looks like this company won't survive this year, they've already laid off so many people.)

9. 天氣預報話有颱風，睇怕聽日嘅旅行要取消。(The weather forecast says there's a typhoon, I'm afraid tomorrow's trip will have to be cancelled.)

10. 佢病咗成個禮拜都未好，睇怕要睇醫生。(He's been sick for a whole week and hasn't recovered, I'm afraid he needs to see a doctor.) [end of text]


